687
00:31:23,510 --> 00:31:24,870
Let's not get separated.

688
00:31:24,870 --> 00:31:25,400
It's fine.

689
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:26,000
No need.

690
00:31:26,740 --> 00:31:27,540
