are indeed married,

701
00:32:15,720 --> 00:32:17,480
but it's a fake marriage.

702
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:18,440
I understand.

703
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:19,770
Like Mr. and Mrs. Smith.

704
00:32:20,270 --> 00:32:21,400
Though compared to Angelina Jolie,

